race.comment: LANCELOT DU LAC (7) nice colt progressing quickly through his grades. Just over a month between runs when taken to the front for a convincing win over this trip at Warwick Farm in BM64 grade. Will take control early from the draw with the 54kg. Can win again in this tougher race. UNLEESHING (9) took ground off Miss Spacegirl two-back, then demolished her rivals by 4 lens over 1550m at Randwick Kensington. Heading in the right direction and shapes as the main danger despite drawing out. AROHA STONE (3) pulled out plenty in the heavy going with a sharp form reversal to score over 1500m at Rosehill. Proven at this level and stays in the mix. PRETTY POWERFUL (5) closed late when third over the 1400m here at latest. Key jockey change and will relish the mile. NKOSI (1) resumes. Showed ability in stronger company last prep and comes to hand quickly. Respect from the draw.
